The ice cream/soda is certainly the star of the show and the reason to come here.
I went standard issue vanilla milkshake and couldn't be happier by wide ordered some pink concoction and was thrilled with it.
My son got a green ninja drink and was wired with sugar delight for the next 3 hours.
I will come back here I just won't order food next time.

